Don't waste your time. There is nothing useful here. This is the free downloadable version with no enhancements. There is no guide as was mentioned. Just the one file. To remove watermark you must buy the full version. (around $80 minimum) 

If you want to buy the software, just go to the site and get the latest version - this one is already old.
There is a guide included which can only be seen when you unzip the file.....
LOL.. How to UnZip an executable?
